                    oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                    oc:textContent "Use this skill to turn structured data (CSV/TSV/JSON) into **clean, reproducible** visualizations using **D3.js**. The goal is to produce **stable outputs** that can be verified by diffing files or hashing." ] ;
